<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-670] DatePatternConverter ISO8601_PATTERN does not conform to ISO8601</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-670</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ISO8601_PATTERN is defined with a space between the date and the time. ISO8601 requires a &apos;T&apos; between the date and the time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12721331">LOG4J2-670</key>
            <summary>DatePatternConverter ISO8601_PATTERN does not conform to ISO8601</summary>
